text.tspan: Time spent sleeping, per day, men vs women
Average minutes spent sleeping per day, by sex (20-74). Estimates come from time use surveys and include one
weekday and one weekend day distributed over the year.
Source: European Commission (2004) - How Europeans spend their time - Everyday life of men and women - Data 1998-2002
